{"tid":1707044,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"各位暴大仔棄裝而唔係收起文具","createTime":"2019-11-11T08:21:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T12:33:31.000Z","uid":59693,"like":28,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"7cdb6f40055860a39f83c8e9e3c8471a08ebbaea","tid":1707044,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:21:24.000Z","msg":"各位暴大仔棄裝而唔係收起文具<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本用酒精抹左指紋同體液棄曬係走廊／垃圾房，班狗搜到都唔知邊間房擲出黎，捉到你地都冇證據告<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加上大量文具集中係公眾地方，混淆之餘，證據可靠性會降低<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你地收起文具，搜到就會證據確鑿，所以大家保障左自己先，文具可以再買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nTLDR: <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">棄裝大於一切</span></span>"},{"pid":"b8d775f29297437274f3994ab912f09b71cb9d2f","tid":1707044,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:21:59.000Z","msg":"心痛暴大，守唔到就要棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16027d310649c29df9ad08aebf1d2de372daff7a","tid":1707044,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:23:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3af31b9a5fc0997b079e0df9b19d1616b396999","tid":1707044,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:24:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />保命緊要呀"},{"pid":"af45aaff88c76f47050fc11a2319f2f3bf195f17","tid":1707044,"uid":205927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:25:15.000Z","msg":"棄啦，最多之後合資比你地買返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\